replyContent: When you finish a game please choose Game Menu, then Main Menu. From here you can go to Single Player and choose a different "Play as" option: alternate who goes first / play first / play second. I'm afraid this is currently linked to piece colour. We will add your suggestion for consideration on our to-do list.
